{"h":[{"d":[{"f":"草被摟到，或被摟草的（作物）。","e":["￹`Makapkapay~ `ko~ `pananoman~.￺￻水田除草了。"]},{"f":"摸索到。","e":["￹`Makapkapay~ `ako~ `ko~ patat`ikor~an `a~ `lalan~.￺￻我摸索著返回的道路。"]},{"f":"指被摸索的（對象）。","e":["￹`Makapkapay~ `ako~ `ko~ `payci~ `i~ `'alofo~ `no~ `paketo~.￺￻在褲袋裡我摸到銅板。"]}]}],"stem":"kapkap","t":"makapkapay"}